Class SafeResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • codebases.types.NamespaceResolver_c

        • codebases.types.SafeResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NamespaceResolver

    public class SafeResolver
extends PathResolver
implements NamespaceResolver
    This resolver preempts lookups to inner by first using the platform resolver. This ensures the platform classes cannot be redefined by a codebase.
    Author:
    owen
